    COMMENT: Returns a string representation of this user.
    METHOD toString(): String
        
        PURPOSE: Provides human-readable user representation
        
        RETURNS: The user's name if present, otherwise the string "null"
        
        WHY: Allows convenient string conversion for logging, debugging, and display
        
        BEHAVIOR:
            COMMENT: Return the user's name if available, otherwise "null"
            IF this.name is not null AND this.name is not empty THEN
                RETURN this.name
            ELSE
                RETURN "null"
            END IF
    END METHOD
